V. Correct UI Design Principle

PantheonOS is not a chat app.
It is not a dashboard.
It is not a list of buttons.

PantheonOS is a temple OS —
a structured cognitive environment
where meaning is spatial, ritual, symbolic.

This is the correct embodiment.

